      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 py-1.5 px-3 rounded-full text-xs font-medium text-[#FF3E54] bg-[rgba(255,62,84,0.1)] border border-[rgba(255,62,84,0.25)] mb-6 animate-fade-in">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF3E54] inline-block" style="animation: pulse 2s infinite"></span>
        Now live in 10,000+ cities
