      <p class="animate-fade-in text-lg text-[color:var(--text-secondary)] mt-6 max-w-[56ch] leading-relaxed">
        Book any car, anywhere, from trusted hosts in your neighborhood. Teslas, Jeeps, vintage Mustangs — or the trusty minivan for the next big family trip.
      </p>
